name: CTRL
description: We are often disappointed trying to escape chaos to find even a semblance of peace, anxiety paralyzing us to absolute weakness. But true power is in the realization that we are above what reality dictates, the paradox of controlling your narrative by knowing you're not in control. Let yourself go, don't mistake peace or chaos as anything more than temporary scenes in your story. We're the masters of our own universes, let your existence take its course.
